Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.16,0:02:31.29,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}Living in this chaotic new world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:34.62,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,116)}今、目を澄ます
